{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "a1b2c3d4-e5f6-7890-abcd-ef1234567890",
    "name": "AlgaPosts",
    "description": "Collection para o sistema distribuído AlgaPosts.\n\n**Microsserviços**\n- `post-service` (porta 8080): API REST de posts\n- `text-processor-service` (porta 8081): processamento assíncrono via RabbitMQ (sem endpoints REST)\n\n**Pré-requisitos**\n1. `docker compose up -d algaposts-rabbitmq`\n2. Iniciar `text-processor-service` e `post-service`\n\nApós criar um post, aguarde alguns segundos para o processamento assíncrono preencher `wordCount` e `calculatedValue`.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Post Service",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Criar post",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status 201 Created', function () {",
                  "    pm.response.to.have.status(201);",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "pm.test('Retorna id UUID', function () {",
                  "    pm.expect(json.id).to.match(/^[0-9a-f-]{36}$/i);",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "pm.collectionVariables.set('postId', json.id);",
                  "pm.environment.set('postId', json.id);"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"title\": \"Meu primeiro post\",\n  \"body\": \"Linha um\\nLinha dois\\nLinha tres\\nLinha quatro\",\n  \"author\": \"Eskokado\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{post_service_base_url}}/api/posts",
              "host": [
                "{{post_service_base_url}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "api",
                "posts"
              ]
            },
            "description": "Cria um novo post, envia para a fila de processamento e retorna 201 Created.\n\n`wordCount` e `calculatedValue` não são retornados imediatamente."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Buscar post por ID",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status 200 OK', function () {",
                  "    pm.response.to.have.status(200);",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "pm.test('Post possui id', function () {",
                  "    pm.expect(json.id).to.eql(pm.collectionVariables.get('postId'));",
                  "});"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{post_service_base_url}}/api/posts/{{postId}}",
              "host": [
                "{{post_service_base_url}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "api",
                "posts",
                "{{postId}}"
              ]
            },
            "description": "Retorna os detalhes de um post. Após o processamento assíncrono, inclui `wordCount` e `calculatedValue`."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Listar posts (paginado)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status 200 OK', function () {",
                  "    pm.response.to.have.status(200);",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "pm.test('Estrutura paginada', function () {",
                  "    pm.expect(json).to.have.property('content');",
                  "    pm.expect(json).to.have.property('page');",
                  "    pm.expect(json).to.have.property('size');",
                  "    pm.expect(json).to.have.property('totalElements');",
                  "    pm.expect(json).to.have.property('totalPages');",
                  "});"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{post_service_base_url}}/api/posts?page={{page}}&size={{size}}",
              "host": [
                "{{post_service_base_url}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "api",
                "posts"
              ],
              "query": [
                {
                  "key": "page",
                  "value": "{{page}}"
                },
                {
                  "key": "size",
                  "value": "{{size}}"
                }
              ]
            },
            "description": "Lista posts com paginação. Cada item retorna `PostSummaryOutput` com `summary` das 3 primeiras linhas do body."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Buscar post inexistente (404)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status 404 Not Found', function () {",
                  "    pm.response.to.have.status(404);",
                  "});"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{post_service_base_url}}/api/posts/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000",
              "host": [
                "{{post_service_base_url}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "api",
                "posts",
                "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000"
              ]
            },
            "description": "Retorna 404 quando o post não existe."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Criar post inválido (400)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status 400 Bad Request', function () {",
                  "    pm.response.to.have.status(400);",
                  "});"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"title\": \"\",\n  \"body\": \"\",\n  \"author\": \"\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{post_service_base_url}}/api/posts",
              "host": [
                "{{post_service_base_url}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "api",
                "posts"
              ]
            },
            "description": "Validação: title, body e author são obrigatórios."
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ],
      "description": "API REST do microsserviço post-service."
    },
    {
      "name": "RabbitMQ (Management API)",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Overview",
          "request": {
            "auth": {
              "type": "basic",
              "basic": [
                {
                  "key": "username",
                  "value": "{{rabbitmq_username}}",
                  "type": "string"
                },
                {
                  "key": "password",
                  "value": "{{rabbitmq_password}}",
                  "type": "string"
                }
              ]
            },
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "http://{{rabbitmq_host}}:{{rabbitmq_management_port}}/api/overview",
              "protocol": "http",
              "host": [
                "{{rabbitmq_host}}"
              ],
              "port": "{{rabbitmq_management_port}}",
              "path": [
                "api",
                "overview"
              ]
            },
            "description": "Verifica se o RabbitMQ está em execução via Management API."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Fila de processamento",
          "request": {
            "auth": {
              "type": "basic",
              "basic": [
                {
                  "key": "username",
                  "value": "{{rabbitmq_username}}",
                  "type": "string"
                },
                {
                  "key": "password",
                  "value": "{{rabbitmq_password}}",
                  "type": "string"
                }
              ]
            },
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "http://{{rabbitmq_host}}:{{rabbitmq_management_port}}/api/queues/%2F/{{queue_post_processing}}",
              "protocol": "http",
              "host": [
                "{{rabbitmq_host}}"
              ],
              "port": "{{rabbitmq_management_port}}",
              "path": [
                "api",
                "queues",
                "%2F",
                "{{queue_post_processing}}"
              ]
            },
            "description": "Consulta a fila `text-processor-service.post-processing.v1.q`."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Fila de resultado",
          "request": {
            "auth": {
              "type": "basic",
              "basic": [
                {
                  "key": "username",
                  "value": "{{rabbitmq_username}}",
                  "type": "string"
                },
                {
                  "key": "password",
                  "value": "{{rabbitmq_password}}",
                  "type": "string"
                }
              ]
            },
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "http://{{rabbitmq_host}}:{{rabbitmq_management_port}}/api/queues/%2F/{{queue_post_processing_result}}",
              "protocol": "http",
              "host": [
                "{{rabbitmq_host}}"
              ],
              "port": "{{rabbitmq_management_port}}",
              "path": [
                "api",
                "queues",
                "%2F",
                "{{queue_post_processing_result}}"
              ]
            },
            "description": "Consulta a fila `post-service.post-processing-result.v1.q`."
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ],
      "description": "Endpoints da Management API do RabbitMQ para monitorar filas e conexões.\n\nUI: http://localhost:15672 (rabbitmq / rabbitmq)"
    },
    {
      "name": "Text Processor Service",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Info",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{text_processor_service_base_url}}",
              "host": [
                "{{text_processor_service_base_url}}"
              ]
            },
            "description": "O text-processor-service **não expõe API REST**.\n\nEle consome mensagens da fila:\n- `{{queue_post_processing}}`\n\nE publica resultados em:\n- `{{queue_post_processing_result}}`\n\nPorta configurada: 8081 (apenas para health interno Spring Boot)."
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ],
      "description": "Microsserviço de processamento assíncrono de texto. Comunicação exclusiva via RabbitMQ."
    }
  ],
